Catch all the Premier League action with Showmax Pro, with live sport streaming to your device, courtesy of SuperSport. There’s a London derby to kick things off as Fulham hosts Arsenal, Liverpool begins their defence of the title against the returning Leeds, Spurs face the Toffees on Sunday and the Seagulls tackle the Blues on the following day. All the English Premier League action is available to livestream at showmax.com or via the Showmax app. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-366998 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EPL-live-on-Showmax-1200x628-1-640x335.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="335" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EPL-live-on-Showmax-1200x628-1-640x335.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EPL-live-on-Showmax-1200x628-1-600x314.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EPL-live-on-Showmax-1200x628-1-768x402.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EPL-live-on-Showmax-1200x628-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Showmax Pro bundles all the good stuff you’ve come to expect on Showmax with music channels, news, and live sport streaming from SuperSport. In South Africa, this includes all the Premier League, UEFA Nations, La Liga, Serie A and PSL games, as well as a wide range of live sport events including athletics, professional boxing, and the world’s biggest marathons. Showmax Pro subscriptions start at R225 per month. Existing Showmax subscribers: New Showmax subscribers: If you already have the Showmax app, remember to update it to the latest version before the big weekend. That way, when game-time arrives, all you have to do is press “Play”. If you don’t have access to Wi-Fi, stream Showmax with data bundles from Telkom, Vodacom, or MTN. To use save data, go into Settings > Preferences in the app and choose the lowest Bandwidth Capping option so you use less data when you stream. The Minimum setting uses just 100MB per hour. This article was published in partnership with Showmax Pro.